<a name="389"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Advanced Display Technologies</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC South Hall 1</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): DisplaySearch </span>
<br/>

<IMG height=142 src="/print/docs/DisplaySearch.jpg" width=263 align=right>
<P>The Advanced Display Technologies TechZone showcases the latest developments in all advanced display technologies from around the world covering a-Si TFT LCDs, LTPS TFT LCDs, AMOLEDs, PMOLEDs, PDPs, flexible, reflective and 3D displays for a wide variety of applications ranging from mobile phones to TVs and more. Come and see the displays of tomorrow that will drive the display supply chain and change the way we view entertainment and information. <BR></P>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="2585"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Casual Gaming</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">South Hall 2</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): MumboJumbo</span>
<br/>

<IMG height=120 src="/print/images/photos/MumboJumboLogo2.jpg" width=158 align=right><BR>The Casual Gaming TechZone at the 2009 International CES, sponsored by MumboJumbo, features companies showcasing the latest titles and games in one of the fastest growing segments in the gaming industry.&nbsp;See companies such as MumboJumbo, Static 2358, and Merit Entertainment all in one location, the Casual Gaming TechZone, within the <A href="/print/exhibits/displays/gamingShowcase.asp">Gaming Showcase</A> in South Hall 2.<BR><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="2451"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Digital Health</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">Sands Expo and Convention Center </span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): Meridian Health</span>
<br/>

<IMG height=118 src="/print/images/content/MH_blu-darkblu2.jpg" width=226 align=right><BR>The Digital Health TechZone sponsored by Meridian Health features emerging technologies and innovative companies using home and person-based options for disrupting the traditional delivery of health and wellness services.&nbsp;See the transformation and creation of new consumer centric connections between patients and healthcare providers.&nbsp;It’s about solving the right problems with best solutions for maximum impact.<BR><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="756"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">DisplayPort</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">Sands Expo and Convention Center </span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): Video Electronics Standards Association </span>
<br/>

<IMG height=72 src="/print/images/content/DisplayPort_web_10-12.jpg" width=283 align=right vspace=10><BR>The <STRONG>DisplayPort TechZone</STRONG> features technology that enables a common interface approach across both internal and external display connections, and makes high-quality audio available to the display device over the same cable and the video signal. Delivering true plug-and-play capabilities, DisplayPort is expected to accelerate adoption of protected digital outputs on PCs to support viewing high definition and other types of protected content while enabling higher levels of display performance. <BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="1926"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Greener Gadgets</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC Central Hall</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s):   </span>
<br/>

<BR><IMG height=119 src="/print/images/photos/greener_gadets_logo_border.jpg" width=283 align=right>The Greener Gadgets TechZone features the pioneering technologies that benefit the environment and sustainability of global economy. The CE industry is reducing its environmental footprint through promoting alternative and renewable energy sources, manufacturing products from recycled materials, using biodegradable/less packaging. The Greener Gadgets TechZone will display the innovations that make it possible for every person on this planet to make use of technology and benefit from growing CE advances.<BR><BR><STRONG>Exhibitors: </STRONG><A href="/print/docs/Greener_Gadgets.pdf"><STRONG>There's still space available to exhibit in this TechZone!</STRONG></A><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="1614"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Mobile Broadband</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC South Hall 4</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): GSM Association</span>
<br/>

<IMG height=208 src="/print/images/content/MBtm_bmk_bk_port_rgb_small.jpg" width=244 align=right><BR>Experience mobile broadband today!<BR><BR>Consumers now have a new Mobile Broadband future - thanks to the GSM-Association initiative creating a new category of always-connected Mobile Broadband devices. The initiative has united 16 of the worlds best known IT and mobile companies under the new service mark helping consumers easily identify ‘ready to run’ Mobile Broadband devices.<BR><BR>The GSMA Mobile Broadband TechZone brings mobile broadband to life. See real life examples from around the world of the speed of Mobile Broadband in action.<BR><BR>Experience the global phenomenon that is mobile broadband live today.<BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="754"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">HDMI</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC South Hall 1</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): HDMI Licensing LLC</span>
<br/>

<IMG height=47 src="/print/images/content/HDMI.jpg" width=200 align=right><BR>High-Definition Multimedia Interface (HDMI) is the acknowledged world standard for connecting consumer electronics products and devices. Utilizing only a single, intelligent cable, users can connect their home theater system without the mess and hassle of multiple cables and cords while still preserving video and audio quality. <BR><BR>The <STRONG>HDMI TechZone</STRONG>&nbsp;features a sampling of the hundreds of companies that have already adopted this evolutionary technology. Come learn how HDMI can provide consumers and manufacturers with this cutting-edge technology by visiting one of the newest TechZones at the International CES, the <STRONG>HDMI TechZone</STRONG>. Here's what you'll see:
<UL>
<LI>High-def video and audio manufacturers </LI>
<LI>High-def hardware manufacturers </LI>
<LI>High-speed service providers </LI>
<LI>Signal processors </LI>
<LI>Semiconductors<BR></LI></UL>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="2316"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">HD-PLC</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC South Hall 1</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): HD-PLC Association</span>
<br/>

<BR>High Definition Power Line Communication (HD-PLC) is one of the best power line technologies for the stable transmission of data because of its high performance, speed and HD capacity. With HD-PLC you can create home networks for Internet, high-definition video and audio, camera monitoring, and more, all without extra wiring. Forget about walls between rooms anymore. No need to worry about making holes for wiring or about walls reducing transmission speed. Simply plug into a wall outlet with your HD-PLC adaptor, and create your home network.<BR><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="753"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">HomePlug</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">LVCC South Hall 2</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): HomePlug Alliance</span>
<br/>

<BR><IMG height=71 src="/print/images/content/HomePlug.jpg" width=225 align=right>HomePlug is an industry alliance comprised of industry leaders at each level of the value chain&nbsp;- from technology to services&nbsp;and content. HomePlug Alliance members bring necessary capabilities and a financial commitment to the successful launch of the technology. Industries include:
<UL>
<LI>Service and content - New services, content to pull demand for network devices, requirements for network to support services, usage models, provisioning, customer care. </LI>
<LI>Retail - Channels for sales&nbsp;and support of networked devices, installation and support services, consumer education. </LI>
<LI>Hardware - Connected devices to enable new classes of services via the internet or other networks&nbsp;- PC, CE, networking. </LI>
<LI>Software - Software services and applications to simplify setup and use of the network. </LI>
<LI>Silicon - Cost effective silicon with a variety of feature sets to support a broad variety of products. </LI>
<LI>Technology - Enabling technology that meets requirements for performance, cost, and is scalable to future generations.</LI></UL>
<P>The alliance's mission is to enable and promote rapid availability, adoption and implementation of cost effective, interoperable and standards-based home powerline networks and products. <BR></P>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="1954"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">i-stage</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">Sands Expo and Convention Center</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s):   </span>
<br/>

<IMG height=132 src="/print/images/photos/istage235.jpg" width=235 align=right><BR>The most disruptive, next-gen tech products, applications and services clamored for a chance to demo at i-stage, the proving ground for revolutionary new technologies, and now they’ve arrived at CES! The contenders represent staggering leaps in gaming, social media, mobile retail, security, telecommunications and 3D video development and have each been vetted by a panel of industry judges at their live demonstrations in Las Vegas.<BR><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="2101"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Robotics TechZone</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">Sands Expo and Convention Center</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s): Robotics Trends</span>
<br/>

<BR><IMG height=107 src="/print/images/content/Robotics.gif" width=120 align=right>CES + Consumer Robotics = CES Robotics TechZone.<BR>For companies to maximize their potential for success in the consumer robotics market, as well as grow the market as a whole, they must be able to identify, meet with and educate prospective customers and partners more effectively and rapidly than their competitors.&nbsp; <BR><BR>The CES Robotics TechZone was designed specifically to do just that.&nbsp; It presents a unique opportunity for companies and individuals to become active participants in a new technology industry poised for massive growth – consumer robotics.<BR><BR>
<a class="back_to_top" href="#">[back to top]</a>
