<div class="sub-content-header">Stevie Wonder and Friends</div>

<span class="techzones-indented">Sands Expo and Convention Center</span>
<br />

<span class="techzones-indented">Sponsor(s):  National Federation of the Blind and Sendero Group</span>
<br/>

<IMG height=64 src="/print/images/photos/Sendero-Group-logo.jpg" width=95 align=right><IMG height=53 src="/print/images/photos/NFB-logo.jpg" width=128 align=right><BR>Meet Stevie Wonder and technology friends and see examples of electronics blind people use in contrast with many they cannot.&nbsp; Try dialing your cell phone with your eyes closed. Learn how minor design improvements can add millions of blind and visually impaired customers to your markets.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR>
