<br/>

<IMG height=44 src="/print/images/photos/Qualcomm_web_7-19.jpg" width=200 align=right>
<P>This TechZone hosts a special exhibition of state-of-the-art mobile devices and applications.&nbsp;<BR><BR>Demonstrations include:&nbsp;</P>
